//      (megakernel_dispatch_arch) installs the Llama arch globals
//      (HIDDEN=2048, HEAD_DIM=64, N_HEADS=32, N_KV_HEADS=8, FF=8192,
//      USE_QKNORM=0, ROPE_PAIR_LAYOUT=1) before any phase emitter runs.
//   4. Wrapping the emitted ISA bytes into a complete .co via the standard
//      multi_code_object path
